metadata.description: The Asgardian warrior Sif was no stranger to battle, but when Asgard and its people made their glorious return through the power of Thor, Sif's body was stolen and possessed by crafty Loki and since, Sif hasn't been her true self. Now Sif sets out with Beta Ray Bill to fight her way back to true warrior's glory!
metadata.name: SIF, Vol. 1
